Description: Attracts large-sized fish and increases your chances of landing one. Occasionally guarantees you will land a large-sized fish. Can be used up to 3 times while fishing, each use increasing the effectiveness and GP cost. May also attract rare species of fish. Can also be used with fish caught using Powerful Hookset. First Use: 10 GP Second Use: 20 GP Third Use: 30 GP

Attracts small-sized fish and increases your chances of landing one. Occasionally guarantees you will land a small-sized fish. Can be used up to 3 times while fishing, each use increasing the effectiveness and GP cost. May also attract rare species of fish. Can also be used with fish caught using Precision Hookset. First Use: 10 GP Second Use: 20 GP Third Use: 30 GP
